x4freetext: Targets Stacks Contining Mylar, Aluminium and Tantalum
Foils of High Purity (99.99 %) Were Irradiated
With 3.65 a*GeV C-12-Ions and 3.65 GeV Protons in an
External Beam of the Dubna Synchophasotron.

x4freetext: . Correction According to Memo Cp-D/216.
Transfor to Usual Reaction Formalizm from
Elem-Mass Formalizm. Reference is Added.
Last checking has been done.
DATE is corrected
.The Errors Assigned to the Cross Sections
Values are Based on Those of Counting Statistics,
Detector Efficiency, and Target Thicnesses, As Well.
The Systematic Error About 10% Corresponding to the
Beam Flux Monitor is not Included.

x4freetext: - By Authors - To Estimate Secondary Particle Induced
Reactions, Product Yields were Measured For "Thick"
[154 Mg.Cm-Sq] and "Thin" [62 Mg/Cm-Sq].
Each Quoted Cross Section is the Weighted Average of As
Many As Five Separate Determinations.
